                            <comment id="13624179" author="mbennett" created="Fri, 5 Apr 2013 23:36:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch to tweak solrconfig.xml to produce some suggestions.  This is perhaps imperfect, given text_general&apos;s processing, but at least it produces some results.  The type textSpell is no longer in schema.xml (not sure if/when it ever was)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13624203" author="mbennett" created="Fri, 5 Apr 2013 23:56:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve also submitted &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4681&quot; title=&quot;Add spellcheck to default /select handler&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-4681&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-4681&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which includes what&apos;s in the patch, plus it adds it to the default /select launch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
